channel.title: Looking For An Experienced Coder
channel.description: Hello Im looking to create another RSPS server. I have created a few in the past but I usually had my friend code, but he doesn't code anymore. If you would like to help me get started with coding or help the server I am planning, I am willing to pay you back in some way. I am open to any rank, monthly payment, donations split, etc. You can reach me quickly on my skype, jakethesnake12345
